                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Following their fourth meeting the Foreign Ministers temporarily adjourned until
                    Monday, September 18, in order to participate in the fifth session of the <gloss
                        target="#t_NATO1">NATO</gloss> Council. For documentation on the Council
                    meetings, see <ref target="#pg_85">pages 85</ref> ff.</p>
            </div>
